If you would like to contribute a paper, please send an abstract immediately.
Each oral presentation lasts 25 minutes, with a 5 minute question and answer
period.  The length of the paper included in the proceedings can vary, but
is typically three to seven pages long.

The deadline for the abstracts is September 30, 1994.

